      "id": 4,
      "title": "Ticket",
      "slug": "ticket",
      "short_description": "Internal helpdesk and issue tracking system for Pilar Group teams.",
      "description": "Ticket is an internal support platform that allows teams across PT Pilar Niaga Makmur to submit, track, and resolve operational issues in one place. It streamlines cross-team communication by replacing ad-hoc messaging with a structured ticketing workflow. Integrated with Pilar Group's central auth via JWT for seamless access. Runs on a local Windows server with Laragon.",
