      "title": "AssetIT",
      "slug": "assetit",
      "short_description": "IT asset management system built on Snipe-IT, integrated with Pilar Group's SSO via SAML.",
      "description": "AssetIT is the internal IT asset tracking solution for PT Pilar Niaga Makmur, deployed using the open-source Snipe-IT platform. It covers the full asset lifecycle — from procurement and assignment to transfers and disposal — giving the IT team a clear view of all company hardware and software. As the only service in the ecosystem using SAML (instead of JWT), it demonstrates the flexibility of Pilar Group's central auth architecture. Runs on a local Windows server with Laragon.",
