      "id": 12,
      "title": "Papertrail",
      "slug": "papertrail",
      "short_description": "Purchase approval workflow system with document number generation for internal procurement and legal processes.",
      "description": "Papertrail is an internal workflow management tool built for PT Pilar Niaga Makmur to digitize and track the purchase approval process across departments. Each purchase request is routed through a structured approval chain — from the originating department through relevant approvers, all the way to the finance team. The system ensures full visibility into request status at every stage, reducing manual follow-ups and miscommunication. In addition to approval tracking, Papertrail includes a document number generator for procurement documents (PP) and legal paperwork, ensuring consistent and traceable document numbering across the organization. Built with Express.js on the backend and React on the frontend.",
      "tech_stack": "[\"Express JS\",\"React.js\",\"MariaDB\",\"Compute Engine\",\"JWT & SAML Auth\"]",
